(47335, 1, '2017-09-23 21:40:45', '2017-09-24 04:40:45', 'I''m Khristian, and first off- thank you for visiting my site! This is a work-in-progress as I learn more and more in my Skillcrush All-Access Blueprint courses!\r\n\r\nTo give you a bit of information about me, I am a 20-something fourth-year undergrad at Washington State University, majoring in Criminal Justice with a minor in Political Science. My studies in Criminal Justice have shown me the importance of learning more technical skills in the realm of programming and coding as cyberattacks become more prevalent (and more difficult to combat).\r\n\r\nIn learning these skills, I have found that my love lies in all things c o d e . I also enjoy visual design, which I am also learning right now, and traditional media. \r\n\r\nThank you for bearing with me while I learn to create an excellent site! :)', 'About Me', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-23 21:40:45', '2017-09-24 04:40:45', '', 2, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2017/09/23/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
