(47351, 1, '2017-09-30 19:23:13', '2017-10-01 02:23:13', 'I am a student at Washington State University studying Criminal Justice and Political Science. I have goals of law school in the near future, and have taken up learning tech skills in hopes of working remotely or as a freelancer (or both!) in order to allow myself to earn the income necessary to keep my family comfortable while also pursuing our dreams together. I have worked in the medical and recreational marijuana industries in Washington state since 2014, and have worked in social media management, retail operations, web design, inventory control, and staff supervisor within this industry alone! \r\n\r\nWhen I am not studying or debugging my code, I am at the gym, walking my German Shepherd, learning French, or painting.', 'Hi, I''m Khristian.<br />I love building websites.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'homepage', '', '', '2017-09-30 19:32:42', '2017-10-01 02:32:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=47351', 0, 'page', '', 0),
