(47365, 1, '2017-10-01 21:55:13', '2017-10-02 04:55:13', '<center>I get how to do this, because I do it for my job! Lucky me!</center>\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-5" src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/17883661_10154752488163401_5115031331569301276_n-240x300.jpg" alt="" width="240" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<justify><font color=green>I am a 28 year old student of both the digital design industry, programming and coding, as well as criminal justice and political science. What can I say, I love to learn! The world is so vast, I want to know everything about it.</font color></justify>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/iconmonstr-instagram-10-64.png" alt="" width="64" height="64" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-47342" />', 'hey what''s up', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-01 21:55:13', '2017-10-02 04:55:13', '', 4, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2017/10/01/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
